StyleAdapter for AudioVid√©oCours website.

Usage information.
Place your ping logo file in the directory "files".
Edit the variable LOGOFILENAME at the beginning of the script.
Modify THEMEPATH and CONFFILE if the website is not installed in the default path.
You can edit MARGLEFT and MARGTOP to place your logo. Beware, MARGTOP is calculated in the script too.
The value in the script are the minimal values.
The maximal values are :
44 + (250 - WIDTH) 
84 + (80 - HEIGHT) for the top margin
Launch the script as root.

Don't forget to change the University Name, Acronym and Link at the end of the script.
